<section id="known-bugs">
  <title>Known Bugs and Limitations</title>
    <para>
    This section lists known bugs and limitations using &app;.
    </para>
    <section id="critical-suspend-action">
      <title>Power consumption when suspended</title>
      <para>
      Your computer still uses a small amount of charge even whilst suspended.
      If "Suspend" is chosen as the policy option for the battery critical low,
      and the power completely runs out when sleeping, your work may be lost.
      See bug <ulink url="http://bugzilla.gnome.org/show_bug.cgi?id=330267" type="http">#330267</ulink> 
      or more details.
      </para>
   </section>
</section>

